text: Inferno is the seventh studio album by Swedish noise rock band Brainbombs. It was released on vinyl LP by Skrammel Records in 2017. A limited edition of 300 copies contained a bonus 7" "Trust Me". == Track list == == References == Category:2017 albums Category:Brainbombs albums Category:Rock albums
